values: well it happened at the worst possible time...i was notified that the army is sending me on a little field trip! well more like an extended field trip. probably to a big sand lot. i dont know for sure where, but i know about when. so much for getting my degree! i was almost there and almost out of the army. oh well.

The tide is not looking too good this week:( this will limit my shore fishing options...however if the south swell dies then i can go fishing from the kayak. surfing is always an option if the swell stays through the week. maybe the best of both worlds... Haleiwa would be 1-3 feet and south shore flat! this is not very likely though. i guess i could go diving...which i would rather be doing somewhere exotic like Palau. that would be sweet! oh well...i will probably sleep. still at work bored out of my mind.

i am at work right now and bored out of my mind! i hate getting up at four am just to go to work...well at least i can make some money. i get three days off this week which is cool but i wish i could get some more hours this week. the sooner i pay off my divemaster course the sooner i can start making some money. i plan on going fishing this week! well i hope i get to go fishing! the marlin are in and there are reports of ahi coming in too! that would be sweet! can anyone say seared ahi? mmm...ahi!
